OL,3,CHealth Department raises concern over
OL,4,Crising painkiller dependency
OL,6,FThe Department of Health has raised
OL,7,Fconcern over a rising dependency on
OL,8,Fsome highly addictive over-the-counter
OL,9,Fpainkillers.
OL,11,FIt comes as a senior addictions
OL,12,Fpsychiatrist based in Belfast revealed
OL,13,Fthat some patients are taking up to
OL,14,Fone hundred strong painkillers a day.
OL,16,FAnd one man told UTV how he almost
OL,17,Fdied after becoming addicted to a
OL,18,Fcombination of Ibuprofen and Codeine
OL,19,Fthat he started taking for migraines
OL,20,Fand a leg injury.
