OL,3,CHealth Department raises concern over
OL,4,Crising painkiller dependency
OL,6,FThe Department of Health said that
OL,7,Fsome over-the-counter medication, such
OL,8,Fas stronger combination painkillers
OL,9,Fcontaining a mixture of paracetamol or
OL,10,Fibuprofen along with codeine or
OL,11,Fdihydrocodeine, can be highly
OL,12,Faddictive.
OL,14,FThe use of these types of painkillers
OL,15,Falmost cost 37-year-old Belfast man
OL,16,FMichael Main his life.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
