OL,3,CHealth Department raises concern over
OL,4,Crising painkiller dependency
OL,6,FMr Main said he started using
OL,7,Fcombination painkillers 12 years ago
OL,8,Fto treat a leg injury and migraines.
OL,9,FAt the height of his addiction, he was
OL,10,Ftaking 64 tablets daily. His weight
OL,11,Fdropped to four stone, he needed
OL,12,Fsurgery for a perforated ulcer and
OL,13,Fseveral blood transfusions.
OL,15,FHe eventually sought medical help for
OL,16,Fhis addiction and has been in recovery
OL,17,Ffor four months.
