OL,3,CHealth Department raises concern over
OL,4,Crising painkiller dependency
OL,6,FBelfast Trust Consultant Addictions
OL,7,FPsychiatrist Dr Joy Watson, who is
OL,8,Fbased in the Malone Place Addiction
OL,9,FServices Clinic, said that addiction
OL,10,Fto stronger combination painkillers
OL,11,Fcan cause serious health issues,
OL,12,Fincluding severe liver, kidney and
OL,13,Fstomach disease and with some people
OL,14,Fending up in Intensive Care Units
OL,15,F(ICU).
OL,17,FShe added: "Sadly, some people have
OL,18,Flost their lives. They can also cause
OL,19,Fissues in patient's personal or work
OL,20,Flives.
