OL,3,CHealth Department raises concern over
OL,4,Crising painkiller dependency
OL,6,F"The good news is, there is treatment
OL,7,Favailable to substitute codeine and it
OL,8,Fis highly effective. The earlier you
OL,9,Fseek the help, the better for your
OL,10,Fhealth. If you are concerned about
OL,11,Fyour relationship with over-the-
OL,12,Fcounter medication, speak to your GP
OL,13,For pharmacist."
